<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV80">
<l>cīrara cāṇṭutaṉ ceṅkōl cilanāḷ celīikkaḻinta</l>
<l>pārara cottu maṟaintatu nāyiṟu pāraḷanta</l>
<l>pērara cēyem vicumpara cēyemmai nīttuvañcitta</l>
<l>vōrara cēyaru ḷāyiru ḷāyvan tuṟukiṉṟatē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Equal to a regent of the earth who, having led an excellent reign,</l>
<l>after a few days have gone by under his just sceptre, passes away, the sun has vanished.</l>
<l>O great king who measured the earth, our great king in heaven, only king who left [and] deceived us,</l>
<l>[your] coming is experienced as grace [and] as darkness.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
